{"tid":251752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海之戀新樓盤外疑代理爭客打架　3女子被捕","createTime":"2017-05-21T07:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T10:57:42.000Z","uid":12342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"987f02c56c0396968329bcc8cf97e9bbd8f0cae4","tid":251752,"uid":12342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"荃灣新盤海之戀示範單位附近的酒店前出現打架情況，疑為地產代理「爭客」出事。下午12時許，3名女子在上址爭執打鬥，其中1名女子報案，警員接報到場調停，將3名分別姓葉(48歲)、姓孫(37歲)和姓陳(25歲)女子，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架拘捕，其後，葉女送院，孫拒絕送院，陳無受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n有地產代理監管局人員其後到場調查。海之戀樓盤為港鐵與長實合作發現的樓盤，售樓處樓下昨日亦發生地產代理圍客、爭客事件。地監局表示，一向關注地產代理在參與一手住宅物業銷售時的操守和秩序，亦會到新盤銷售處巡查，但局方不會評論個別樓盤的情況。 <br />\n<br />\n根據地監局指引，地產代理在進行一手住宅物業銷售活動時，不可有過分推銷的行為，例如阻礙行人，即使途人表明沒興趣購買該物業，仍然不斷游說及向其招攬生意等。"},{"pid":"43ccdfe4ae8caaf3c1084f2ab66eda5c2a68afaf","tid":251752,"uid":12342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/mobile/bkn-20170521143425237-0521_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170521%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170521143425237-0521_00822_001.html&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9929ecb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/mobile/bkn-20170521143425237-0521_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e9bc373d8ec8870f0b62fee79664faa436520034","tid":251752,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864433a55e68e763f416f8564fcdbaf8c51796d2","tid":251752,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"3隻雞爭著同人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9126d3fa12d90